Airbnb Data Analysis Project 
Documentation 
1. Project Title 
Airbnb Listings Analysis & Revenue Insights Dashboard 
Prerna Patil 
2. Project Overview 
This project analyzes Airbnb listing data to identify patterns in occupancy, pricing, revenue 
generation, customer ratings, and neighborhood performance. 
The objective is to transform raw Airbnb listing data into meaningful business insights using 
Python for data cleaning & EDA and Power BI for dashboard visualization. 
The final dashboard helps stakeholders understand: 
 Revenue performance 
 Occupancy trends 
 Property type distribution 
 Neighborhood listing performance 
 Pricing patterns and review behavior 
3. Business Problem 
Airbnb hosts and property managers need insights to: 
 Identify high-performing neighborhoods 
 Understand pricing vs revenue relationships 
 Analyze customer review patterns 
 Optimize property type offerings 
 Improve occupancy and revenue 
Without structured analysis, decision-making becomes difficult. 
