12. Business Recommendations 
Based on the analysis: 
1. Focus on High-Demand Neighborhoods 
Hosts should prioritize locations like Sydney and Liverpool where listing demand is high. 
2. Improve Guest Experience 
Listings with higher reviews tend to attract more bookings. 
Improving guest experience can increase occupancy. 
3. Optimize Pricing Strategy 
Hosts should balance price and review ratings to maximize revenue. 
Overpricing without strong reviews may reduce bookings. 
4. Diversify Property Types 
Although entire homes dominate, private rooms may attract budget travelers and increase 
occupancy. 
